		</div>
		<div style="padding: 5px; margin:5px;" >
			자유게시판<a href="/client/menu/insert/comunity/border/free/list"><img src="/resources/images/list_icon.png" style="float: right;" /></a>
			<div style="width:380px; height:180px; border-top-width: 1px; border-top-style: dotted; padding-top: 10px;overflow:hidden; ">
			
